{"tid":1016983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[2倍本地人口] 黃金周結束 訪澳𨳊旅客逾121萬人次 按年增26.6%","createTime":"2019-02-11T06:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T06:58:37.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"23af3d594cbf1c003317396f39a2c47ffb349d9c","tid":1016983,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T06:58:37.000Z","msg":"好多蝗去 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>澳𨳊</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cms.exmoo.com/uploads/2019-02-11/mPednrOtftx7FMOlNahN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.exmoo.com%2Fuploads%2F2019-02-11%2FmPednrOtftx7FMOlNahN.jpg&h=5258e1e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（春節黃金周7日總訪澳旅客統計。）<br />\n<br />\n（黃金周7日訪澳內地旅客數據。）<br />\n<br />\n春節黃金周於昨（10）日結束，旅遊局公布數據顯示，由農曆年三十至年初六共7日，總訪澳旅客逾121萬人次，按年增幅26.6%，其中，年初三(7日)訪澳旅客人次最多，達22.6萬人次，按年上升22.6%。<br />\n<br />\n至於訪澳內地旅客方面，黃金周則共有89.9萬人次，同比增加25.6%。<br />\n<br />\n（編輯：盧妙雯）"}]}